ABOUT THE APP

This program uses OO programming to create a Bookshop App.

Features of Version 1 of "THE BOOKSHOP APP"

1. You can have a digital inventory of all books currently available in your store( all the book titles and the number of copies available)
2. You can add reviews to each of the books so as to aid customers make a choice of the books to buy
3. Once the user inputs the number of books wanted, the total price is displayed..

## There are some features of this app that have been highlighted in the main.cpp file and that will be implmented in THE BOOKSHOP APP 2.0
